files.description: 921-page data dictionary documenting the Crystal PM B.10 EHI export. Covers 55 database tables exported as CSV files, with column-level documentation (name, data type, description, extraction method) for every field. Includes serialized .NET object model documentation for eye care-specific data types (visual acuity, refraction measurements). Tables span patient demographics, clinical records (20+ ehr_file sub-types), billing/HCFA claims, VSP vision insurance, optical inventory, scheduling, documents/images, and patient engagement.
